based on gnome-settings-daemon-3.4.2

注意
background插件正常运行要求Nautilus不托管桌面

*Dependence (Debian)

**deepin-desktop

**sudo apt-get install libxml2-dev

**sudo apt-get build-dep gnome-settings-daemon 来直接判断依赖, 下面列出的依赖
可能不完整
sudo apt-get install libtool gsettings-desktop-schemas-dev \
libgnome-desktop-3-dev liblcms2-dev libnotify-dev libgnomekbd-dev libpulse-dev \
libcanberra-dev libcolord-dev libcanberra-gtk3-dev libwacom-dev libxtst-dev \
libupower-glib-dev libgudev-1.0-dev libcups2-dev libgconf2-dev

*Install
aclocal --force
autoconf
autoheader
automake --add-missing
./configure --prefix=/usr
make
sudo make install
